data.description: Make this beautiful home in the City of Conroe your own just off SH105 and a few miles from Lake Conroe. Built in 2020. This lightly used home has 5 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, Game room,     study, Huge backyard all located on a cul-de-sac lot. No direct neighbors behind for privacy, Open-concept floor plan with large family, dining and Island kitchen. stainless steel appliances, Light and modern colors make this a very livable and great place to call home. Act Quickly, this will not last long.
